Rand, McNally and Company's new business atlas map of California
New business atlas map of California
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Shows railroad lines and electric rail lines overprinted in red ink.
In lower left: "Copyright, 1910, by Rand McNally & Co." and "Copyright, 1906, by Rand McNally & Co."
Inset maps: San Francisco and vicinity -- Los Angeles and vicinity -- San Diego and vicinity.
Includes indexes to principal cities and overprinted list of railroads keyed to map by number.
